                            <comment id="15715977" author="olegk" created="Fri, 2 Dec 2016 19:09:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This one turned out to be not so easy. There were two options how to fix the problem for individual routes: by making &lt;tt&gt;#getStats&lt;/tt&gt; method iterate through the entire global request queue thus making it expensive under load or by maintaining an extra structure per each route to keep track of route specific requests and making every lease / release operation a bit more expensive but keeping  &lt;tt&gt;#getStats&lt;/tt&gt; method cheap. I opted for the former.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fixed in SVN trunk and 4.4.x branch. Please review / re-test.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oleg  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
